{"tid":648050,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"講真啲蝻細細個已經係地方惡霸","createTime":"2018-04-30T10:52:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-30T12:42:45.000Z","uid":182474,"like":17,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"472da52a0d13f5ed336db80af47c5db85eaee5c9","tid":648050,"uid":182474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T10:52:34.000Z","msg":"早幾日見有個小學蝻(樣似中二三)同一個廿幾嘅蝻<br />\n個小學蝻仲着住校服 但掛咗條幼金鏈係頸<br />\n兩個都係行路串串貢 un吓un吓咁<br />\n佢地個陣就上緊樓梯<br />\n有個啊伯迎面落樓梯 扶住條欄杆慢慢行落去<br />\n個小學蝻見個啊伯阻住佢行路<br />\n就戚起個身 睥住個啊伯 想凶9佢<br />\n個啊伯唔敢睥翻佢<br />\n隻小學蝻覺得自己好型<br />\n仲要指住個啊伯 屌左聲<br />\n<br />\n過左陣又見到有一大班小學蝻行樓梯<br />\n個個攞住碌板球棍係到fing嚟fing去<br />\n起初冇留意點解無啦啦咁嘈<br />\n後尾聽到佢地係到用啲唔鹹唔淡嘅廣東話講晒粗口咁<br />\n望一望 見到佢地指著後面係到鬧<br />\n但又見唔到有人<br />\n過多幾秒 見到個香港細路係後面托住部滑板車🛴<br />\n想跟著班蝻<br />\n班蝻見佢追過嚟 笑9個細佬之後跑走咗<br />\n個細路上完樓梯 個樣好委屈咁踩住部車追班蝻<br />\n點解要咁犯賤痴埋去俾人bullying<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n記得以前細個已經驚左班蝻<br />\n試過俾班廿幾歲嘅蝻 <br />\n困住係個氹氹轉到<br />\n好大力係咁轉<br />\n隔離有個細佬仲俾人轉到飛咗岀去<br />\n跌到損晒<br />\n細個已經成個惡霸咁<br />\n大個都唔知會變成點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95d7c98084ed7ffeba5427563a25d3251f3eecc3","tid":648050,"uid":182474,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T10:54:37.000Z","msg":"可能屋企附近多<br />\n成日都見到呢啲事"},{"pid":"91529cea4e0e4724331bcaf3d2398f8ec1fd555f","tid":648050,"uid":25221,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T10:55:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"28db8f96b76360f018cd86ef7245f155b66c928b","tid":648050,"uid":41508,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T10:55:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"92a8e3f79883c45c0068de4a13622c2f92441aa8","tid":648050,"uid":182474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"91529cea4e0e4724331bcaf3d2398f8ec1fd555f","tid":648050,"uid":25221,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T10:55:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T10:57:11.000Z","msg":"細個真係好鬼驚佢地<br />\n大個見到好反感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e43659cc81e5880bfb5b37da3748c7791f7807d","tid":648050,"uid":41508,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T10:57:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"eda2e0913fa9b9abfd2b5a626d9e99a9a562c1e2","tid":648050,"uid":182474,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"2e43659cc81e5880bfb5b37da3748c7791f7807d","tid":648050,"uid":41508,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T10:57:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T10:59:58.000Z","msg":"咁大方嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我會屌到佢飛起<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但唔夠膽 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n驚佢吹雞<br />\n團結就是力量"},{"pid":"9338770dbe7dd0c2e49cc84138125f55bbb7a70b","tid":648050,"uid":41508,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T11:03:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"31ac7febe618fdf6d48c0d7eb8204ebbc472ed44","tid":648050,"uid":182474,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"9338770dbe7dd0c2e49cc84138125f55bbb7a70b","tid":648050,"uid":41508,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"eda2e0913fa9b9abfd2b5a626d9e99a9a562c1e2","tid":648050,"uid":182474,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"2e43659cc81e5880bfb5b37da3748c7791f7807d","tid":648050,"uid":41508,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T10:57:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T10:59:58.000Z","msg":"咁大方嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我會屌到佢飛起<br />\n<br />\n<b